3. Routine Setting
Defines philosopher actions (eating, sleeping, thinking).

philo_routine(philo) â†’ Main routine executed by each philosopher thread.
take_forks(philo) â†’ Locks both forks before eating.
lock_forks(philo, left_index, right_index) â†’ Ensures proper fork locking order.
eat_philo(philo) â†’ Philosopher eats, updates time, and increments meal count.
sleep_philo(philo) â†’ Philosopher sleeps for time_to_sleep.
think_philo(philo) â†’ Philosopher enters thinking state.
